{"tid":1590553,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[左膠和理非入]屋企人：對話平台應該要積極報名搶晒啲位合唱願榮光","createTime":"2019-09-23T18:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T06:00:24.000Z","uid":57911,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6a540f85eb7da129c39cb9f85e90dd4c45f27053","tid":1590553,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:46:18.000Z","msg":"屋企人尋晚諗到個好爆嘅idea<br />\n既符合和理非又符合杯葛對話平台<br />\n200萬人全力搶晒對話平台啲位<br />\n林鄭柒婆埋位就開始合唱願榮光<br />\n口罩紗布係容許帶入場<br />\n唔係舉牌叫口號唔會俾人趕出場<br />\n全場齊和唱佢耐你唔何<br />\n仲可以令林鄭柒婆冇癮兼落佢面<br />\n上到報之餘又做到文宣行到出國際<br />\n騎劫之餘又可以阻擋林鄭柒婆玩一言堂<br />\n<br />\n唯一壞處：要用真身登記，只適合左膠參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ebdd47527ef9032e9e44edefc3a5b71e083eae","tid":1590553,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"a97909bd7c73cdda0427d86381c131a3bcba77e8","tid":1590553,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:48:28.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f2c2c1171c7b48e675c640bee6503c5cdd06a74b","tid":1590553,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:48:51.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"b0da1476de55c2d5b9168cf80dc256643d1ddf69","tid":1590553,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:49:16.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"3476b4177841c2e85295bdd86d1ebddeb10fc0c4","tid":1590553,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:49:50.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9622d74003f23b60c04cbb7ae1fc400f07d026c9","tid":1590553,"uid":232619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:50:11.000Z",